{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow vehicles over 40 years of age to display a black and silver number plate.",
        "additional_details": "40 years of age makes a vehicle officially a historic vehicle, and therefore it already has a different status under law, allowing it to be tax and MOT exempt. The black and silver number plate would serve as a visual indicator of its changed status.",
        "background": "New legislation from the government has changed the precedent that vehicles over 40 years of age are able to display a black and silver number plate. I want this to be reverted, so any historic vehicle that is tax and mot exempt (over 40 years old) can display the black and silver plates.",
